  • Field Details

    • _isBad

      private Boolean _isBad
      A boolean variable indicating whether the button is an elimination button or not. If true, it is an elimination button; otherwise, it is not.

    • _isActive

      private Boolean _isActive
      A boolean variable indicating the active status of the button. If true, a player is allowed to press it in the game and it responds appropriately; otherwise, the button does nothing.
